Class Job

  • java.lang.Object
    • ch.pschatzmann.docker.jobs.model.Job
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Runnable

    public class Job
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Runnable
    Instance which is executed as scheduled job. For each job we need to execute at least 1 command step. We record the job id so that we can cancel the job again.
    Author:
    pschatzmann
